item.title: 【Requests】[REQ VID] - boomtown rats - i don't like mondays
item.description:
i really like the music video to this song.
all the youtube uploads i've seen have bad audio and/or video (watermarks, cropping, compression artifacts).
it doesn't need to be upscaled, i just want a relatively hq version with cdq audio so i can enjoy it.
there's also an extended version where the first verse repeats; either one is fine.

thanks !
item.author: k_o
